OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy and breezy throughout
OL,6,Fthe day as outbreaks of rain move
OL,7,Feast, these heavy at times with a
OL,8,Fchance of thunder. Some drier and
OL,9,Fbrighter spells in the west later in
OL,10,Fthe afternoon as the rain clears away.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining largely cloudy with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of occasionally heavy rain
OL,14,Fthrough the evening and overnight.
OL,15,FIncreasingly dry and clear spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping from the west towards
OL,17,Fmorning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
