OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FAny cloud and rain in the east
OL,6,Fat first will soon clear to sunny
OL,7,Fspells in the morning. Bright spells
OL,8,Fand a few showers in the afternoon,
OL,9,Fheavy at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,12,For sunny spells and scattered showers
OL,13,Fon Tuesday and Wednesday, heavy and
OL,14,Fthundery at times. Widespread cloud
OL,15,Fand rain arriving from the west on
OL,16,FThursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
